🔗 RELATIONSHIPS (MENTAL MODEL)
User → Tenant (1:1 optional)
User → Roles (many-to-many)

Property → Units (1:N)

Unit → Leases (1:N over time)
Tenant → Leases (1:N)

Lease → Billings (1:N)
Lease → Payments (1:N)

Unit → Maintenance Requests (1:N)
Tenant → Maintenance Requests (1:N)
